### ----------------------------
POST http://localhost:5000/api/work
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Prepare investor pitch deck",
  "description": "Slides for VC demo including traction, revenue, and burn",
  "priority": "high",
  "dueDate": "2026-01-20"
}

###


### ----------------------------
### 3️⃣ Get my work items
### ----------------------------
GET http://localhost:5000/api/work
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###


### ----------------------------
### 4️⃣ Upload a startup document
### ----------------------------
POST http://localhost:5000/api/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MyBoundary

--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="workItemId"

6963722d52f59f3e0dfbbc08
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="startup.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

This is a sample startup document.

Revenue: 2.5L INR  
Expenses: 1.2L INR  
Funding Required: 5L INR  

Major Risks:
- High marketing spend
- Customer churn
- Cash flow issues

--MyBoundary--

